---
layout: layouts/page.njk
permalink: /lab-members/
heroImage: /assets/images/banner-members.jpg
title: Lab Members
eyebrow: The team
intro: A group of scientists building tools and asking how the brain gives rise to perception.
---

{% from "components/cards.njk" import memberCard %}

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    {% for group in members.groups %}
      <div class="people-group">
        <h2 class="people-group__title">{{ group.title }}</h2>
        <div class="people-grid {% if group.id == 'pi' %}people-grid--lead{% endif %}">
          {% for person in group.people %}
            {{ memberCard(person) }}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}

    <p class="people-foot">
      Many former members have gone on to faculty positions, industry, and beyond.
      <a href="/alumni/">Meet our alumni →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
